{"tid":86551,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"同事已走，想升職的我ot到凌晨還未夠","createTime":"2017-01-19T07:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T07:48:44.000Z","uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c4991b480b66910e19a7a57ba196aea6ec5b199","tid":86551,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"同事已走，想升職的我ot到凌晨還未夠，攰過街尾果隻狗。<br />\n疼痛在頸背後，說我能紮職未來在我手，做到幾點可以抖？<br />\n同事會走，剛收工的我哭乾眼淚靜靜自修，寂寞因此牽我手。<br />\n原來我收工以後，我只得到了沒有。<br />\n但老細至少往後，成為刻薄狗。<br />\n<br />\n閉起雙眼我想有補水，眼睛張開枱面得杯水，感激老細佢，尚有稱讚六句讓我滿足到落淚。<br />\n補不補水也會屌7誰，早不早走這天總過去。<br />\n奮鬥為了永不失去，誰勉強愚弄過誰。<br />\n遞信難以放進房裡，何不將這封信放進心裡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5ff92c637ab0193e056d421f558ff15bee707a","tid":86551,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"樓主邊間教會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe6de62f81177617383e116fb91007c9f447aca","tid":86551,"uid":20528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"哈姆太郎？"},{"pid":"6e5e6c6be4395d5e8db6d32d43b6ca2bea697866","tid":86551,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"OT就升你咩？"},{"pid":"bfc775f5dac564504d3f31ff670ce448515e6161","tid":86551,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"暴君 心裡感謝神？"},{"pid":"bc0315cf5bdad46dfaeebc5b83b12bc68c733993","tid":86551,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"阿門。"},{"pid":"2f585ef6e0341e2a44ed25712b3e82467acffd13","tid":86551,"uid":44408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"聖詩班啱曬你"}]}